V0204_01_00_00_0.text: I want to know what I'm truly capable of.

V0204_01_00_00_1.text: So I won't let you stop me!

V0204_01_00_01_0.text: I no longer need the strength of my curse.

V0204_01_00_01_1.text: This mark was the cause of all my suffering.

V0204_01_00_02_0.text:
I learn something new every Duel.
What'll I learn this time?

V0204_01_00_03_0.text:
Every Duel hinges on a crucial moment.
I must stay focused.

V0204_01_00_04_0.text: Yusei, I want to know everything.

V0204_01_00_04_1.text: What you see, what you feel during a Duel!

V0204_01_00_05_0.text: I want to earn your trust.

V0204_01_00_05_1.text: So watch what I can do!

V0204_01_00_06_0.text:
Sure, Leo.
Let's see if you learned any new moves at school.

V0204_01_00_07_0.text:
Don't worry about going easy on me, Luna.
Give it your all!

V0204_01_00_08_0.text: As a Signer, I will defeat the Dark Signers!

V0204_03_00_02_0.text:
Here I go!
It's my turn!

V0204_03_00_05_0.text: I can't let fear overtake me...

V0204_05_00_00_0.text: If I believe in myself, I can change the future!

V0204_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0204_08_00_00_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Fragrance Storm!

V0204_08_00_01_0.text: I activate the Field Spell, Black Garden!

V0204_08_00_01_1.text: Flowers shall bloom by feeding on the monsters' energies!

V0204_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Magic Planter!

V0204_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Wonder Clover!

V0204_08_00_05_0.text: The Spell Card, Seed of Deception!

V0204_08_00_05_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 2 or lower Plant from my hand!

V0204_08_00_06_0.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Raging Mad Plants!

V0204_08_00_08_0.text: The Equip Spell, Thorn of Malice!

V0204_08_00_10_0.text: The Equip Spell, Mark of the Rose!

V0204_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Wicked Rebirth!

V0204_08_00_14_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Doppelganger!

V0204_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Half Counter!

V0204_08_00_16_0.text:
I reveal my Trap!
Blossom Bombardment!

V0204_08_00_17_0.text: I flip over my Trap Card, Nature's Reflection!

V0204_08_00_17_1.text: I reflect your effect's damage back to you!

V0204_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Urgent Tuning!

V0204_08_00_19_0.text: My Trap Card, Plant Food Chain!

V0204_08_00_20_0.text: I activate my Trap Card, Star Siphon!

V0204_08_00_21_0.text: The Trap Card, Wall of Thorns!

V0204_09_00_04_1.text: Resurrect by sending the top card on my deck to the Grave!

V0204_09_00_06_0.text: Please use your effect to help me, Stardust Dragon!

V0204_09_00_07_0.text: Stardust Dragon's effect returns it to my field!

V0204_09_00_12_0.text: I regrow this card by banishing a Plant from my Graveyard!

V0204_09_00_14_1.text: When it's Synchro Summoned, all cards are destroyed!

V0204_09_00_17_1.text: When it destroys a Plant in battle, you take 300 damage!

V0204_09_00_20_0.text: Black Rose returns a Special Summoned monster to your hand!

V0204_09_00_21_0.text: Witch of the Black Rose's effect!

V0204_09_00_22_0.text: Rosaria, the Stately Fallen Angel activates its effect!

V0204_09_00_26_0.text: Queen Angel destroys the monster with the lowest ATK!

V0204_09_00_28_0.text: I activate Rose Archer's effect from my hand!

V0204_09_00_28_1.text: By sending her to the Grave, I negate and destroy your Trap!

V0204_09_00_29_0.text: I added Rose Fairy to my hand!

V0204_09_00_29_1.text: Since that was due to an effect, I can Special Summon her!

V0204_09_00_30_0.text: Rose Lover's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0204_09_00_30_1.text: By banishing her, I Special Summon a Plant from my hand!

V0204_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0204_13_00_00_0.text: I Summon my Wall of Ivy!

V0204_37_00_01_0.text: The hopes of the world coalesce into a single star!

V0204_37_00_01_1.text:
Let's rev it up!
Synchro Summon!

V0204_13_00_06_1.text:
Yusei...
With your power by my side, I have nothing to fear!

V0204_37_00_02_0.text: This thorn hunter hides in the sacred forest!

V0204_13_00_09_0.text: I present to you - Violet Witch!

V0204_37_00_03_0.text:
A cold flame envelops the world!
Black flower, bloom!

V0204_37_00_04_0.text: This pure rose blossoms under the quiet moonlight!

V0204_13_00_20_0.text: I Summon the Tuner Monster, Witch of the Black Rose!

V0204_13_00_21_0.text: Arriving from the beginning of creation!

V0204_13_00_22_0.text: I Summon Tytannial, Princess of Camellias!

V0204_13_00_25_0.text: I Summon the Tuner Monster, Twilight Rose Knight!

V0204_15_00_02_0.text: You best get out of my way!

V0204_16_00_00_0.text:
I won't let up!
I'll keep pushing forward!

V0204_19_00_12_0.text: Feel the fury of my Black Rose Dragon!

V0204_19_00_17_0.text:
I'm not done!
Rose Tentacles can keep attacking!

V0204_19_00_24_0.text: Attack, Witch of the Black Rose!

V0204_19_00_25_0.text: Go, Rosaria, the Stately Fallen Angel!

V0204_28_00_00_0.text: I feel as free as the wind!

V0204_28_00_01_1.text:
Friends who believe in me!
And I won't let them down!

V0204_28_00_02_0.text:
I can't stop here.
I have to keep improving!

V0204_28_00_03_0.text: I no longer need to use my cursed power.

V0204_28_00_04_0.text: You taught me that my power is a gift and not a curse.

V0204_28_00_05_0.text: I'll hold up my end, so I'll never let the team down!

V0204_28_00_06_0.text:
I win, Leo.
You gotta study harder.

V0204_28_00_07_0.text:
Don't forget - we're a team.
So let's get stronger together!

V0204_28_00_08_0.text:
I never had friends... until now.
So I'll fight for them!

V0204_29_00_01_0.text: At this rate, I'll never be on Yusei's level...

V0204_29_00_02_0.text: My friends have faith in me, but I let them down...

V0204_29_00_03_0.text: You showed me that I have much to improve as a Duelist.

V0204_29_00_04_0.text: This mark doesn't make me a witch - it makes me special.

V0204_29_00_04_1.text: Thanks for teaching me that, Yusei.

V0204_29_00_05_0.text: I may have lost, but I will come back stronger!

V0204_29_00_06_0.text:
Well done, Leo!
Seems you're keeping up with your studies!

V0204_29_00_07_0.text:
Wow, Luna!
You totally beat me!

V0204_29_00_08_0.text: So this is... the power of the Dark Signers...

V0204_30_00_02_0.text: I have a bad feeling about this...

V0204_33_00_01_0.text: I won't let power overtake me!

V0204_34_00_01_0.text: That's right. I'm the Black Rose.

V0204_34_00_02_0.text:
Dealing pain is fun...
Incredibly fun!

V0204_34_00_06_0.text:
With all this speed...
What's this I'm sensing?

V0204_34_00_07_0.text: Only a Duelist knows how this feels!

V0204_36_00_03_0.text: Yusei! With you by my side, I'm not scared of anything!

V0204_36_00_04_0.text: Yusei! I need you to take care of this!

V0204_36_00_05_0.text:
I'm sorry, Yusei.
I couldn't do a thing.

V0204_36_00_06_0.text:
I believe in Team 5D's!
Let's win this!

V0204_36_00_07_0.text: Show them the power of teamwork!
